      *  SET OF CHECK KEY  *
      *--------------------*
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    FLG     1
     C           BETM      IFEQ 0
     C                     MOVE '*'       FLG
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    FLG
